dc_title_s: Historic Digital Orthophoto Quads Index Grid - Panchromatic DOQ Index Grid: Maryland
dc_description_s: This is a MD iMAP hosted service. Find more information on http://imap.maryland.gov. This database provides map specific details for the 1-meter resolution 1998 panchromatic digital orthophoto quarter quad (DOQ's) distributed by the Maryland Department of Natural Resources such as the file name, quarter quad name, source of the photography, and date of the source photography. Map Service Layer:http://imagery. geodata. md. gov/imap/rest/services/DOQs/DOQIndexGrids/MapServer/1
